CHICKEN + TUNA

Additives:

Carrageenan, Hydroxypropyl Distarch Phosphate, Taurine, Isomaltooligosaccharide, Vitamin A Acetate, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Calcium D-Pantothenate, Vitamin D3

CHICKEN + SALMON

Ingredients:

Water, Chicken, Salmon

Additives:

Carrageenan, Hydroxypropyl Distarch Phosphate, Taurine, Isomaltooligosaccharide, Vitamin A Acetate, Vitamin B2, Niacin, Calcium D-Pantothenate, Vitamin D3

Date Printed is MANUFACTURING DATE.

Expiry 2 years from MANUFACTURING DATE

FEEDING GUIDE ( Cat’s Weight )

0.5 – 1.0 kg : Feeding Amount (50 – 90 g / day )

1.0 – 3.0 kg : Feeding Amount ( 90 – 200 g / day )

3.0 – 4.0 kg : Feeding Amount ( 200 – 250 g / day )

> 4.0 kg : Feeding Amount ( > 250 g / day )

**The amount fed can be adjusted according to your cat activity level. Feed your cat by divided all daily meals into 2 or more servings and ensure fresh clean water is available at all times.

STORAGE:

Store in a cool place. After opening, please consume as soon as possible. If it is not finished, please sealed & refrigerated, and consumed within 2 days.

item.content:encoded:
Baju Raya Kucing Jantan

This Baju Raya Kucing (Teluk Belanga Sampin) is for Male cats (Jantan).

It is equipped with a tailored cutting modified from traditional Malay costumes for cats, so they will feel comfortable and refreshed while wearing the Baju Melayu. The Premium Quality Koshibo Fabric and Sampin Songket make elegant attire for cats during Raya.

Material: Koshibo Fabric

(It is lightweight, breathable & has greater durability, so it is very suitable for cat clothing.)

This color is well as matching set wear (Baju Raya Sedondon) since cats are also our lovely family members, and we celebrate Raya with our cats.

Cloth and Sampin color:

– Royal Green (with Silver White Sampin)

Size chart in inch (“):

• M: Neck (8″) / Chest (15″-18″) / Waist (17″-20″)

• L: Neck (10″) / Chest (18″-21″) / Waist (20″-23″)

• XL: Neck (12″) / Chest (21″-23″) / Waist (23″-24.5″)
